text: Sin Cara is the ring name of two former WWE wrestlers (luchadores): * Místico (Luis Ignacio Urive Alvirde), the first Sin Cara from 2011 to 2013 * Hunico (José Jorge Arriaga Rodríguez), the second Sin Cara (or Sin Cara Negro), who shortly replaced Místico in 2011 and performed as Sin Cara from 2013 to 2019
title: Sin Cara
